com.brightcove.player.media

Interface PlaylistListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ErrorListener

    public interface PlaylistListener
extends ErrorListener
    PlaylistListener identifies objects that expect to receive a Playlist object from an asynchronous operation. Note that on a successful operation, onPlaylist() should be called, however, this interface extends ErrorListener, and if there is an error in the operation, onError() should be called.

    • Method Summary

      Methods
